metadata.name: Love Birds
metadata.description:
It is an digital painting created on procreate..

About Me: Full time software professional, part time artist without any formal training in drawing. I work on all medias such as watercolor, acrylic, pencil sketch and digital art forms though favorite is Pencil sketch. I love painting portraits. I also work on home decors like dreamcatchers

Artist:Aishwarya Saha
